）","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"06c2dae8c7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：张惠英。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"0847da300f","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"c889bf1faf","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你多大？（张答）","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"08f91f9470","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：黄建强。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"00b42eaed6","type":"paragraph","text":"黄：我。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"89250d7936","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：多大？","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"a781162c02","type":"paragraph","text":"黄：十五。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"3fb97ddbaa","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你更小。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"77a2cb459e","type":"paragraph","text":"（顺次点名，问姓名、单位、年龄）","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"f2a3ad8647","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：李春荣。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"af807b9b02","type":"paragraph","text":"李：我。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"47b348b561","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：高个子，山东的。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"dbefac0bef","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：（指康老）两个山东的高个子。（众笑）（依次点名）","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"81c47cde39","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：都是北航的。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"afcce5249c","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：都是“反革命”。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"1328e3cc18","type":"paragraph","text":"（总理点名时，诸首长评论同学们的高矮）","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"b20607f2c8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：张苗苗。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"b903038bfd","type":"paragraph","text":"张：我。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"a7c453d95a","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：多大？","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"6c86cc28d5","type":"paragraph","text":"张：十五。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"6f90cdbc43","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（对众首长）她名字叫苗苗。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"7095d861fc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：北京占多数。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"319d303436","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：想听听你们的意见。刘贤权同志来了嘛？张江霖同志来了嘛？","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"69ce0b0006","type":"paragraph","text":"（刘、张回答）","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"8a9c8ce912","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们自由了！你们解放了！","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"7fecab1c0d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：刘贤权同志多大了？","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"17f6f3bc8c","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：五十二。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"ccc72f9e9c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：张江霖同志多大了？","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"e7a62f161b","type":"paragraph","text":"张：五十一。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"eb1d003bfb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：刘贤权你哪儿人？","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"3cb1892a7c","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：江西吉安。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"330585c84f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：张江霖哪儿的？","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"994a0cd23a","type":"paragraph","text":"张：四川。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"5a977a63a4","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：我都没有听过你们的诉说，今天我们都来了，文革小组、军委的同志来听你们意见，你们讲吧，青海的同志讲，不要重复。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"a27c885579","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们讲一讲吧！","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"0244d8c667","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（对张惠英）你讲讲吧！","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"878071164c","type":"paragraph","text":"（张惠英开始叙述二·二三事件见闻，在讲到被赶到报社大院里时。……）","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"6c2cc486e5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：多少人？","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"65ce855e19","type":"paragraph","text":"王相喜：一千八百多人。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"e41561694c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：报社原有多少人？","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"0666d9125b","type":"paragraph","text":"众：二百人左右。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"ea56e3e4ff","type":"paragraph","text":"（张惠英继续叙述，在讲到关于烧死人的问题时）","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"4546d88662","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：是不是烧死的？","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"1f33319691","type":"paragraph","text":"（张回答。我也没见过烧死的人什么样，烧的腿一面烂了，另一面还挺好的……总理边听边点头）","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"e2b4e222f1","type":"paragraph","text":"（当张讲到持枪者威胁：“你再瞪眼睛，我把你的眼珠子挖出来”时，康老冷笑）","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"45c7737ae5","type":"paragraph","text":"（当张叙述到八·一八被迫跪了一大片人时）","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"e914c98442","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有多少人？","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"97597e3ba5","type":"paragraph","text":"（张回答，并继续叙述暴徒毒打八·一八革命派情况）","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"8bea000b4f","type":"paragraph","text":"（杨成武同志进来）","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"309f1945fc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们的同学有死了的没有？","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"1a445fd3b1","type":"paragraph","text":"（张指陈存秀说）他弟弟被打死了！","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"9bb2e055a8","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你弟弟叫什么？","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"e0a922fd60","type":"paragraph","text":"陈存秀：陈存宣。","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"fccc0d7c99","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（你们哪一位知道得更详细一些，补充一下。","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"bb855dcf89","type":"paragraph","text":"（于桂梅同学补充，当她谈到守卫报社时）","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"153daab75a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有多少人？","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"ca8f7a3d68","type":"paragraph","text":"于：有两千人。","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"74de0fbdbe","type":"paragraph","text":"（康老对总理作解释）","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"7741a03fd0","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们都在里面？","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"f37aa1d168","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：他们都睡在里面，很拥挤。","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"9bcf419440","type":"paragraph","text":"（杨植霖同志于二十一时三十分进入厅内）","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"71cb46b8bc","type":"paragraph","text":"（于继续叙述，当她谈到八·一八革命派被迫用绳子捆绑下跪时）","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"10c273b88b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：（对江青）他们竟敢不执行八条！","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"8b7fcfe262","type":"paragraph","text":"（于继续叙述，当说到八·一八革命派被押解到省委时）","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"6b07f47b72","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：省委？","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"e9f52f8b38","type":"paragraph","text":"于：由省委干部审问，审问的全是平时造反精神最强的。……我们在雪地上冻了一夜，有的工人几天也没吃，我们看到省委干部审问，这完全是反扑，过去被斗的，起来斗造反的。保皇派斗争造反派，一些中……都不敢讲话了。一些当权派纷纷倒向保皇派。那几天在大街上抓人、打人是很严重的。","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"63e6eb6ea7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：事后你看到被打死多少人？","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"d88b107c12","type":"paragraph","text":"（于继续叙述，讲到北桥头死人时）","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"51f57afe30","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：桥头在报社外面？","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"931fe9dc94","type":"paragraph","text":"关锋：那儿死人最多。","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"50737f25bf","type":"paragraph","text":"张江霖：在报社西北角。","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"148f197cd1","type":"paragraph","text":"（于继续叙述）","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"b2bd9fdda2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你在离桥头不远的地方？（于继续叙述）","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"d4adc67c09","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：保卫报社的有多少人？","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"1d81675cca","type":"paragraph","text":"（回答）","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"80a3597add","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：二十多所学校，有多少人死了？","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"cdb6e73df7","type":"paragraph","text":"××：不清楚，消息都封锁了。","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"b882c4d988","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们都什么时候离开的？","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"c7487209e3","type":"paragraph","text":"××：二十四日。陈代海：我是三月六日离开的。","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"6035ba6e52","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：有人抓到军队监狱里没有？","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"2cad850b17","type":"paragraph","text":"（王相喜叙述情况，说明监狱很大）","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"322aaba3c9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那么大？国民党留下的，还是我们修的？","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"22530f9f05","type":"paragraph","text":"（张江霖、王相喜分别回答）","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"2b8d2c40c4","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：在哪儿？","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"20a2770fbc","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（对周总理）他们都在一个房间里。","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"3d90e85ddf","type":"paragraph","text":"（王继续叙述，讲到军人宣传“改过自新、重新做人、前途光明”的内容时，戚本禹同志冷笑。当王讲到外地同学被关押到党校时）","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"caa6778534","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：多少人？","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"27e8b2025c","type":"paragraph","text":"王相喜：四十几个人。……","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"40f61d4bb5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么地方？","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"452c7b0867","type":"paragraph","text":"（王继续叙述党校内状况）","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"2b105e987e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：外地同学有被打死的？","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"43b0bb8e8c","type":"paragraph","text":"（王继续叙述，说到《火车头》用锤子击伤员时）","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"7ef7858ec7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你知道的一死一伤……","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"0ac509d647","type":"paragraph","text":"（王叙述到和军区赵永夫、××等发生争执时）","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"cc53eeb3ca","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们和军区谈判的情况怎么样？","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"e8a03136cf","type":"paragraph","text":"（张金莱详细叙述谈判经过）","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"02597408ee","type":"paragraph","text":"（杨成武同志小声对曹轶欧同志说：“赵永夫在搞鬼！”）","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"fc3ce8b8cf","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：军队哪天武装游行？","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"de8d88cdd2","type":"paragraph","text":"（王滨友、胡长生详述武装游行事）","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"9c53dffd05","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：多少辆军车？（指二·三军队游行）","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"ba18ba0f3a","type":"paragraph","text":"（回答：二百五十多辆）","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"087a9e820b","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：二百五十多辆？！","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"4aa8fb76fb","type":"paragraph","text":"（胡长生谈到有公安厅车子时）","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"68c6e85d0b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：公安厅几个车？","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"a41c7fe2a1","type":"paragraph","text":"（回答）","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"fbec105f9e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：张江霖同志，你们几号来的？","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"d61fcf995c","type":"paragraph","text":"（回答：三月九日）","index":110,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"fdbae9d70a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你知道15号搜枪的事？","index":111,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"2d992533a6","type":"paragraph","text":"（张回答，在谈到二月三日武装游行是支持了右派，打击了左派时，总理不住点头）（当张谈到王文英在谈判时被赶回来时）","index":112,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"0d219568b7","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：赵永夫去了。","index":113,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"386c9e481b"},{"id":"df19ef8e5a","type":"paragraph","text":"（当时叙述到事态继续发展，要发生流血事件时，总理点头）","index":114,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleI